$ Stellarium API: StelMovementMgr.setFlagTracking

Toggles object tracking on or off and goes to the selected object (see → Wissenschaft/Astronomie/tools/Stellarium/script/API/core/selectObjectByName[`core.selectObjectByName()`]).

code {
StelMovementMgr.setFlagTracking(true|false);
code }

gh|about-Stellarium|/API/StelMovementMgr/setFlagTracking.ssc||

sa:

  `core.moveToObject()`

? The time it takes for `setFlagTracking()` to complete its «auto move» operation can be set with `StelMovementMgr.setAutoMoveDuration()`.

  → Wissenschaft/Astronomie/tools/Stellarium/script/API
